highlights.text: MC 張天賦 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “東邪” is the highest at #17.

“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1509 days straight.
“NPC的一場意外” by 陳卓賢 Ian is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 115 spots at #81.
